The paper deals with the problem of an autonomous agent learning about the capabilities of an unknown robot based on its appearance and experimentation. This involves aspects of robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
